                                                                                        <a href="https://github.com/knpuniversity/symfony/edit/master/knpu/ep2-fundamentals/config-parameters.md" target="_blank" class="btn btn-default btn-circle pull-right js-tooltip" title="Edit on GitHub"><span class="fa fa-pencil"></span></a>
                                                                    <p>Congrats! We've basically mastered Symfony configuration and environment system.
But there's just <em>one</em> more trick it has up its sleeve.</p>
<p>Look closely inside <code>config.yml</code> file: one of the settings - <code>default_locale</code> - is
set to a strange-looking value: <code>%locale%</code>. Huh.</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="11353f1718">
